{"tid":2005150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧：中共1月3日下令銷毀病毒樣本 (6/5/2020)","createTime":"2020-05-07T02:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T07:07:46.000Z","uid":134093,"like":341,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"4b06875d4b44cd26d09c5740717a671dbcb48857","tid":2005150,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbxVeCa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbxVeCa.jpg&h=997a7df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">週三（5月6日），美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Michael R. Pompeo）在國務院主持新聞發布會。(KEVIN LAMARQUE / POOL / AFP)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中共瞞疫 造成全球陷入公衛危機</strong><br />\n他在開場白中長時間說明中共瞞報的情形，他說：「128天前，武漢中心醫院急診室醫生艾芬，在網絡首次分享一名病患感染類似薩斯（SARS）病毒相關信息，她的同事李文亮醫生在網絡上與同行分享她的（檢測）報告。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中共衛健委下令銷毀病毒樣本</strong><br />\n「然而中國（中共）沒有這樣做，它們掩蓋了武漢的疫情，其國家衛健委（National Health Commission）在1月3日下令銷毀病毒樣本，讓勇於發出警告的中國公民『失蹤』，利用宣傳機構譴責那些要求透明的人。」<br />\n<br />\n「今天，已經過了120天，中方仍然拒絕與我們分享確保人類安全所需要的信息，例如病毒分離株、臨床標本以及2019年12月多位COVID-19（中共肺炎）患者的詳細信息，更不用說『零號患者』了。」<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/5/6/n12088357.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F5%2F6%2Fn12088357.htm&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=f9dccd35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/5/6/n12088357.htm</a>"},{"pid":"297a6f020e099f6a7ce3ca74d87b8f77d5b4aab5","tid":2005150,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09774fb4b7f042402a145e841772f53d9f359ac6","tid":2005150,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2798d75dc33087870e9d20e4d1457607c36623","tid":2005150,"uid":134093,"